    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "June 30, 1953",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "Federal Bureau of Investigation",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "Washington, D. C.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "Gentlemen:",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "A relative of mine living in Circleville, Ohio has advised me of the following",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "account.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "Two years ago a respected farmer living near Circleville saw a lighted object",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "dancing around, flying around in the air near him late at night in a pasture",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "or field, -- a flying saucer. In due time this came to have general knowledge",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "in the community, and about one year ago the story appeared in the Circleville",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "newspaper.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "Since then he is presumed to have been consulted with representatives of the",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "F.B.I., so it is said there, and only three weeks ago or so it is said the F.B.I.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "representatives came to consult with him again. This time they brought pictures",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "to show the farmer of various types of these flying saucers or space ships that",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "have been apprehended by the government from time to time, and the farmer was",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "able to identify one of them as the type of thing he had seen two years ago.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "The farmer was told, as the story goes, by your representatives, that the par-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "ticular flying saucer he identified is the type that is known to have been fl-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "own from the planet Mars, and that similar ships have been captured, and that",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "your agency or the government hold captive one man at least in California who",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "was taken from one of these things from Mars. This Martian it is understood is",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "now being taught how to speak English -- in California -- and taught American",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "customs. It is said that it is apparent that this Martian comes from a civ'l",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "much more advanced than our own civilization.... and that this account has gen-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "knowledge as reported here in that community.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "I understand that the farmer is a Mr. [REDACTED], that he is held in very high",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "repute in the community, prosperous, conservative and of presumed sound mind.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
